#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.31:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Dānavagga"
msgstr "4. Giving"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Paṭhamadānasutta"
msgstr "31. Giving (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.31:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhimāni, bhikkhave, dānāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these eight gifts."

msgctxt "an8.31:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.31:1.3"
msgid "Āsajja dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr "A person might give a gift after insulting the recipient. "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.4"
msgid "bhayā dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr "Or they give out of fear. "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.5"
msgid "‘adāsi me’ti dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr "Or they give thinking, ‘They gave to me.’ "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.6"
msgid "‘dassati me’ti dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr "Or they give thinking, ‘They’ll give to me.’ "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.7"
msgid "‘sāhu dānan’ti dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr "Or they give thinking, ‘It’s good to give.’ "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ pacāmi, ime na pacanti; nārahāmi pacanto apacantānaṃ dānaṃ adātun’ti "
"dānaṃ deti,"
msgstr ""
"Or they give thinking, ‘I cook, they don’t. It wouldn’t be right for me to "
"not give to them.’"

msgctxt "an8.31:1.9"
msgid "‘imaṃ me dānaṃ dadato kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchatī’ti dānaṃ deti, "
msgstr ""
"Or they give thinking, ‘By giving this gift I’ll get a good reputation.’ "

msgctxt "an8.31:1.10"
msgid "cittālaṅkāracittaparikkhāratthaṃ dānaṃ deti."
msgstr ""
"Or they give thinking, ‘This is an adornment and requisite for the mind.’"

msgctxt "an8.31:1.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dānānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the eight gifts.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.31:1.12"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
